Extract product data from e-commerce URL.

Uses Tavily Extract API with advanced depth to get:
- Product title, description, price
- Ratings and review counts
- All product images
- Category and brand information

Images are optionally downloaded and stored in Supabase Storage.

Returns:
    ExtractResponse with structured product data
